@node History "Announce v2.0 Documentation"

History
~~~~~~~
1.0  (1993-08-04) First release. It was then called 'AnnounceLogon'.

2.0  (1994-04-24) Release version. The tool name was changed to just
     'Announce' because I added logoff notification.

     Messages are queued until the user becomes idle.

     Messages are now sent without going via ARexx.

     There are more news but I'm too lazy to describe them all.

@endnode

